const Create = () => {
    return ( 
        <form>
            <label>Name: </label>
            <input 
                type="text"
                required
            />
            <label>Hours: </label>
            <input 
                type="number"
                required
            />
            <label>Minutes: </label>
            <input 
                type="number"
                required
            />
            <label>Rating: </label>
            <input 
                type="number"
                required
            />
            <label>Numbers of reviews: </label>
            <input 
                type="number"
                required
            />
            <label>Price: </label>
            <input 
                type="number"
                required
            />
            <label>Image : </label>
            <input 
                type="file"
                required
            />
            <button>Add Movie</button>
        </form>
     );
}
 
export default Create;
